    public interface TimeseriesGenerator
extends Generator<java.util.List<org.apache.commons.math3.util.Pair<java.lang.Double,java.lang.Boolean>>>
    Interface for any generator which generates a time series, taking the form of a list of double values (e.g. a score), each paired with a boolean value (e.g. pass/fail).
    Author:
    Geoffrey Neumann, Jerry Swan
